    <h1>Roof Replacement Cost Calculator (North Texas, 2026)</h1>
    <p class="rv-lead">Most Dallas–Fort Worth homeowners pay <strong>$9,500–$18,000</strong> for a full asphalt-shingle roof replacement in 2026 — roughly <strong>$4.75–$7.50 per square foot installed</strong>. Class 4 impact-resistant shingles (the hail-belt favorite) run $12,000–$18,000, and standing-seam metal $18,000–$35,000. Estimate your roof below.</p>
